name: THE NAMELESS ONE
description:
SUNDAY. 10:48 PM.

Akari hears faint whispers from the dark depths of her mind:

"The Nameless One will return when the stars align.

Insanity will rule over all.

Nothing can be done to avoid this fate.

Time and space will end with a scream."

Are these messages coming from inside her head?

Is she going crazy?

How can she make it STOP?
